{"tid":894154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁家傑將赴法談「一國兩制」　冀說服歐洲議會續信香港","createTime":"2018-11-08T07:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T12:28:04.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":220,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3fda312a960b36f05877ea82026f91a54e7170","tid":894154,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:28:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁家傑將赴法談「一國兩制」　冀說服歐洲議會續信香港</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n公民黨主席梁家傑兼資深大律師梁家傑將應邀前往法國史特拉斯堡，出席歐洲議會全會，向各黨派介紹「一國兩制」在香港實踐的情況。梁家傑於今日《明報》撰文，指香港作為熟悉中國、受歐盟信任、自主又有別於中國的世界貿易組織成員，可助歐盟在進行中歐貿易期間建立預警系統，並於中國違規情况時妥為善後。以此游說歐洲議會為他此行的重要任務，如能說服歐洲議會繼續垂注和信任香港，會是「不枉此行」。<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑指出，美國與歐盟在2001年支持中國加入世貿，原意是想透過貿易，使中國成為基於規矩秩序行事，並以民主制度保障國民的人權、自由和貫徹法治精神的國家，但歐美這17年來對中國屢發怨言，「原來互利的想像變成中國獨佔利益的現實」，而人權、自由、民主、法治各方面亦只見領導人「口惠而實不至的空談」。他認為，「中美貿易戰就像積累多年的怨氣一次過爆發」。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港，當年沒有參與中國加入世貿的談判，故對歐美今天所作指控無從置喙。不過梁家傑強調，「香港一直循規蹈矩，在中歐貿易瓜葛中不該殃及無辜」，更何況根據「一國兩制」保住一個與歐盟分享相類價值，以及實施近似制度的香港，對歐盟亦有好處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/262897/【貿易戰】梁家傑將赴法談「一國兩制」%e3%80%80冀說服/?fbclid=IwAR3Vtcq1G2yBtpOqeaDIBL6XZXYnDB7HTWZHw38N5E4rayXQ9wN_NwlVq5M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F262897%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E5%82%91%E5%B0%87%E8%B5%B4%E6%B3%95%E8%AB%87%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E3%80%8D%25e3%2580%2580%E5%86%80%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Vtcq1G2yBtpOqeaDIBL6XZXYnDB7HTWZHw38N5E4rayXQ9wN_NwlVq5M&d=r6fwtmX7qDVnlrJ%2B%2Bqz20%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3c03b280\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/262897/【貿易戰】梁家傑將赴法談「一國兩制」%e3%80%80冀說服/?fbclid=IwAR3Vtcq1G2yBtpOqeaDIBL6XZXYnDB7HTWZHw38N5E4rayXQ9wN_NwlVq5M</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6ede9e8628738ed987ff1f61f0c9b3d1e349da","tid":894154,"uid":52006,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"中共說客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0ced862117479d49c7539ed62822459128e433","tid":894154,"uid":53379,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"quote":{"pid":"6a6ede9e8628738ed987ff1f61f0c9b3d1e349da","tid":894154,"uid":52006,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"中共說客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:32:50.000Z","msg":"呢個動作完全幫緊中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ab3baa9373de3bdd9249f5a8230fe363dfc1c5","tid":894154,"uid":48735,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將心比己, 人地以前信香港係因為信你套制度,信你透明度同法治<br />\n而家3樣都無哂, 當你真心膠假膠咩都好,<br />\n你係歐洲議會你見到香港政府咁樣仲信唔信呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bae400bb532447cdc7831482bd0eba31ce72f5d","tid":894154,"uid":76745,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"對呢班上晒岸既人黎講 維持現狀過埋下半世係最好  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9c61fd09b1b82724b5a32630a73c73bf6fa882","tid":894154,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440565e9b84ce56cb84135bbdf9701481fb2e6a8","tid":894154,"uid":63909,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-siz